## [0.1.1] — 2026-04-23

**Tag:** `v0.1.1` · **Previous:** initial import (`c5f56c3`)

### Highlights (from history up to this tag)

- Library scaffold, Vite dual build (ESM/CJS), demo app, GitHub Pages + CI workflows
- Modal, Signup, Login, Confirm components; WCAG-oriented forms and styling
- Package rename to `@steinshy/wealthhealth-modal`, lint/format/config hardening

### Fixed

- Password and confirm-password inputs stretch full width inside their flex wrapper (`width: 100%` on `.input` in SignupModal and LoginModal CSS modules)
- ConfirmModal demo no longer blocks with `alert()` after confirmation; modal closes after a short async delay
- GitHub Pages build sets `VITE_BASE_PATH` so assets resolve under the repo sub-path
- GitHub Pages workflow runs on both `main` and `dev` branches

